{"tid":2219484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佛山一番街｜山寨澀谷暗藏穿崩位 日本達人：抄襲到個空殼內裏沒靈魂","createTime":"2020-09-27T01:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T07:14:55.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5581d9e6a8b70e040d18de498ee10d5252d444","tid":2219484,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_2BSn2a44lmTaj8xPythjwLgoOg=/802x768/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UJS7ENRRD5EURPCS5ERAYH2NWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_2BSn2a44lmTaj8xPythjwLgoOg%3D%2F802x768%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUJS7ENRRD5EURPCS5ERAYH2NWI.jpg&h=15ca9a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（新增：內容）「好想去日本！」熱衷於外遊的港人，在武漢肺炎疫情下或許不難聽到身邊朋友經常發出如此「悲鳴」。不過，居住在廣東佛山市的民眾，近日即使不能出國，也能體驗遊日感覺，事關佛山市直接將整條東京澀谷六丁目「一番街」移植到當地，街上滿滿的日文招牌、紅綠燈、巴士站等都「抄」得似模似樣，有不少內地年輕人更特地穿上日本校服和Cosplay服飾前來「打卡」。不過，只要仔細一看，就會發現停在路上的日本的士竟然不是右軚，可謂一大「穿崩位」。日本旅遊作家林慧美對《蘋果》表示，驟眼看來，佛山「一番街」的確可以假亂真，但山寨景點只是抄襲到一個空殼，內裏沒有靈魂，特定的社會環境與文化根本「山寨」不來。<br />\n<br />\n這條「山寨」一番街，位於佛山市南海區金沙洲，近日成為許多內地網民「打卡」的熱點。據曾經到過該處的網民形容，佛山「南海一番街」位於兩座高樓之間，總長約100米，日式招牌林立，但上面所寫的日文幾乎都是動漫遊戲作品，如《ONE PIECE》、《名偵探柯南》、《新世紀福音戰士》等出現過的地方或店舖名字。置身其中，的確有一種恍如遊覽東京澀谷的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，網上近日充斥不少佛山「南海一番街」的畫面，其中居住在佛山市從事汽車用品製造工作的舞川老師（@dancingriver），也親身到現場探訪，並在Twitter發文描述所見。<br />\n<br />\n舞川老師指，他發現許多喜好Cosplay的年輕人在該處拍照，「可見日本流行文化在中國年輕世代是多麼的盛行」。他還在一間「藤原豆腐店」外自拍。而「藤原豆腐店」就是《頭文字D》主角藤原拓海的家經營的豆腐店。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p30mG1AY_yY599o4qlPIMOeHvZk=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3YYWWL2HHREFHJM4KU6VNL2HQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp30mG1AY_yY599o4qlPIMOeHvZk%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3YYWWL2HHREFHJM4KU6VNL2HQE.jpg&h=a80ba8fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舞川老師又謂，該處的巴士站、的士站及停車場等都真實呈現澀谷六丁目的面貌，並指幾乎可以假亂真。而他以前是東京都營巴士路線的常客，當看到由澀谷到新橋的「都06」巴士站牌，亦難掩興奮地站在站牌旁合照。<br />\n<br />\n不過，也有網民表示，只要仔細一看，就會發現停在路上的日本的士竟然不是右軚，可謂一大「穿崩位」。也有網民指，只要看到地上的垃圾，就知該處根本是中國。<br />\n<br />\n日本旅遊作家林慧美表示，近日在Facebook看到有很多佛山「南海一番街」洗版，「但我覺得click入去睇嘥咗我嘅時間，快速咁睇咗十幾張相，但我冇仔細睇啲招牌，驟眼看來都似，睇咗『停車』嗰個字係做得似嘅，因為始終都係山寨，我梗係睇正貨啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rNx-lpy8e0oU-s0y__UAvG-STzU=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZPKBBFDYSFEH3L5CSKTK7LAN6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrNx-lpy8e0oU-s0y__UAvG-STzU%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZPKBBFDYSFEH3L5CSKTK7LAN6M.jpg&h=f3684ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/o_8n8mySWSjxd662MJgYAtE2xDI=/802x602/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EKFFJN4X6JE7LGKXNCSTOKTNLY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fo_8n8mySWSjxd662MJgYAtE2xDI%3D%2F802x602%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEKFFJN4X6JE7LGKXNCSTOKTNLY.jpg&h=db1a0a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OkfQXYKTWanhNeuYcquYjzt4JQg=/802x602/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PRL4F4OIIVAPFDQ563QTTIKBIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOkfQXYKTWanhNeuYcquYjzt4JQg%3D%2F802x602%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPRL4F4OIIVAPFDQ563QTTIKBIA.jpg&h=38d8393c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/924WuWbCGj-rALP9HFV2hrPvbV4=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5ZI47DAEIFGMRHMSXR3ZIC6TEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F924WuWbCGj-rALP9HFV2hrPvbV4%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5ZI47DAEIFGMRHMSXR3ZIC6TEY.jpg&h=34c6080a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林慧美不諱言，部份中國人喜歡日本，「但係佢哋係鍾意日本嘅物質，唔係文化囉。」過往，內地也山寨不少外國著名景點，「有呢樣嘢其實唔奇囉」，而山寨景點只是抄襲到一個空殼，內裏沒有靈魂，特定的社會環境與社會根本「山寨」不來。<br />\n<br />\n「我覺得所有根基都喺文化、風土裏面，我當比薩斜塔copy去第二度，其實都係得個殼。」林慧美笑言，如果內地人想暫時以視覺效果「慰藉」一下也未嘗不可，但這情況未必能維持下去。<br />\n<br />\n居港13年的日本人Lena則指，「南海一番街」看起來很有趣，如果拆開每一部份像真度頗高，但以商業街整體來看則有點不同，「因為唔會咁密集&hellip;&hellip;（招牌）有一、兩個睇嚟怪怪地，但都ok接受到。」Lena坦言，只是佛山一個景點目的地，她不會選擇到訪當地，「因為我都唔係animation fans（動畫迷）。」<br />\n<br />\nFacebook粉絲專頁「情熱北海道」的版主情小姐（丁蓓）向《蘋果》稱，細心看招牌那些字體隔開、畫布的質感，還是富有中國特式的日本風，但看得岀中國人的努力。她說：「中日漢字混在一起相信也是特別創造的風格，唯一稍嫌不足之處是地下滿是垃圾。」"},{"pid":"7fd931f8af778545cab31703ade32099e59230c2","tid":2219484,"uid":312470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:56:44.000Z","msg":"見到幅圖都形住有陣中國臭味飄出黎"},{"pid":"ae59a2da1a46b071dfba21ae55d76d06421d68eb","tid":2219484,"uid":302070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"無論邊個地方抄其他地方都係得個殼冇靈魂㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684c19a5ad363b7ae1184588120155b82f0dbbed","tid":2219484,"uid":40171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"單單隨地掉垃圾呢樣嘢就算畀多50年時間，中國人都唔會改得到"},{"pid":"8cd6d1710dadfcb54129a4f9c161afccd5bdae19","tid":2219484,"uid":122202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:10:05.000Z","msg":"睇標題就知係蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a9ff33f5a4f24e4f4fd4b7d579c6a779466344","tid":2219484,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:16:25.000Z","msg":"其實唔討論先係最好抹殺佢既方法<br />\n有d為講而講"},{"pid":"8e6059d89f0dd66efeb0f06f54df81e479283347","tid":2219484,"uid":241628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:18:53.000Z","msg":"將幾個縣ge 野當晒係澀谷真係好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到鐮倉高校前係個咁ge招牌<br />\n直頭係侮辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063528283020595f45a0e58c1b8e1639c1e98315","tid":2219484,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:45:02.000Z","msg":"幾年前揸住 Sony 相機影抗日，家下就連條街都 dup 埋出嚟，民族主義根本得個殼，自己文化無嘢留戀年青一代全部外求。"},{"pid":"ddfd2f3c16ec4a468ddcbd2a808581f687fef136","tid":2219484,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0280d3f59608b4a04447f6fc2a5e17e95209e1ba","tid":2219484,"uid":19990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:14:55.000Z","msg":"近鏡睇有啲位似旺角花園街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，尤其係小食檔奶茶檔"}]}